content.p: How to gain access to our corporate applications. Kinetics (KX) is the University's Corporate Application used to manage Student Accommodation, Conference Administration and Catering Bookings FM:Interact is the University's Corporate Application used for Space Management Free at point of use To access Kinetics, please download and complete the Kx Access Request Form, also available via Workspace. Once authorisation has been granted, raise a support request via the Self Service Portal. Your login details will be emailed to you once your access has been set up. The KX application will then be available from UoN Applications. To access FM:Interact, follow the link below, staff can access using their University password and login Detailed instructions are available on the links below (Workspace log in required): Kinetics (Workspace) FM:Interact If you're struggling please get in touch with the team Submit and track requests to solve your IT issues Updates on the University's core IT services
